{"tid":1557741,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［緊急］中共預告911將於香港重演","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:46:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:58:47.000Z","uid":172093,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3dbce1b59450c2abeef8cb3f819182a45a9bcdd","tid":1557741,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:46:37.000Z","msg":"中共喉舌China Daily今日獨家預告明天美國國殤911事件記念日 將於香港重演911贈慶 並企圖嫁禍香港和平示威者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/0LV9cYcGC8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F0LV9cYcGC8&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=f9f5e05d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/0LV9cYcGC8</a><br />\n<br />\n聲明如下<br />\n1）連登仔有本事打自己隻飛機 無本事劫機<br />\n2）撐自由民主示威者嘅國泰員工都俾中共迫到停飛哂<br />\n3）連登仔做嘢又會俾你中共喉舌獨家爆料啦 on99<br />\n4）我地親外國勢力，唔會在人地傷口灑鹽<br />\n<br />\n講完。<br />\n<br />\n不如大家諗下，到底四圍幫中共散播hate speech嘅港龍CEO，到底喺中共重演911度，扮演咩角色？<br />\n<br />\n連登仔唔知 拉登都唔知<br />\n既然係咁<br />\n大家一齊篤灰一齊去問個清楚明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港太古集團有限公司(公共事務部) - (publicaffairs@swire.com)<br />\n2. 國泰航空employee_questions@cathaypacific.com<br />\n3. 鄧健榮 ,國泰航空行政總裁(augustus_tang@cathaypacific.com)<br />\n<br />\n4. FAA e-form<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.faa.gov/about/office_org/headquarters_offices/aae/programs_services/faa_hotlines/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.faa.gov%2Fabout%2Foffice_org%2Fheadquarters_offices%2Faae%2Fprograms_services%2Ffaa_hotlines%2F&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=fa12ff87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.faa.gov/about/office_org/headquarters_offices/aae/programs_services/faa_hotlines/</a><br />\n<br />\n5. ICAO<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp; icaohq@icao.int<br />\n<br />\n6. ICE <br />\nHRV.ICE@ice.dhs.gov<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ice.gov/webform/hsi-tip-form\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ice.gov%2Fwebform%2Fhsi-tip-form&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=b3cd6a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_